Principles Of Christian Churches You Need To Know

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XHOmBV4js_E

We believe it’s important to have a new members’ class at every church. These classes are supposed to be designed to give you a greater understanding of the principles, scriptural and spiritual guidelines that a community follows. The lessons are being outlined progressively in order to help with your knowledge of our church, as well as of who The God is, what He teaches us and how you can praise His Name and Word.
